## EA proprietary game assets — NEVER commit these.
## The `original/` directory holds the user's local Generals Zero Hour install
## (Generals.dat, *.big archives, Activation.dll, EA shaders, audio, models).
## These are proprietary EA content protected by copyright; even on a private
## GitHub repo this should not be uploaded.
/original/

## Internal working docs — plans, dev-logs, handoff notes. Kept locally only,
## out of the public repo (may reference local paths / other projects).
/internal/

## AI assistant config (user-specific)
/.claude/
/CLAUDE.md

## IntelliJ, CLion, etc.
/.idea

# IntelliJ-style CMake bits
cmake-build-*/

## Ninja
.ninja_deps
.ninja_log
build.ninja

## Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc

## Build / run artefacts (logs, vcpkg cache, etc.)
*.log
/logs/
/vcpkg_installed/
.flatpak-builder/